Seems like you expect League to let you have that juicy 15:0 win streak but it's not like that.

If you actually play good every game and impact the game positively, you can slowly (but surely!) climb even if you have some trolls here and there. That doesn't matter. As long as you focus on getting better as a player overall, its all fine my dude :D 


